        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令閻浮提請雨國內。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "降澍大雨使令充足莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又說呪曰。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "野邏野邏(一)逸利逸利(二)喻屢喻屢(三)樹屢樹屢(四)嗜利嗜利(五)社邏社邏社社邏(六)求茶求茶求求茶(七)伽茶伽茶(八)耆遲耆遲(九)呵邏呵邏(十)醯利醯利(十一)牟漏牟漏(十二)多邏多邏(十三)帝利帝利(十四)兜漏兜漏(十五)阿那阿那(十六)陀呵陀呵(十七)鉢遮鉢遮(十八)祁利祁利(十九)醯那醯那(二十)求利陀(二十一)末利陀(二十二)鉢囉末利(二十三)彌勒菩薩告勅令除一切雨障莎呵又說呪曰。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛提佛提(一)浮佛提浮佛提(二)令諸眾生持佛功德。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "除滅一切障業重罪。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而說呪曰。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "陀羅尼(一)馱離(二)輸婆摩帝(三)求那伽囉鉢囉鉢泥(四)摩呵若奴盧枳(去聲五)輸說羅(引)達彌(六)薩底夜波羅(引)底若(七)摩訶耶那殊(引)瑟[口*致](八)阿殊(引)瑟[口*致](九)盧歌[口*耶](引)瑟[口*致](十)婆伽婆帝佛陀彌帝隷(十一)阿鉢羅夜薩婆差多羅尼(十二)叔訖離施(十三)卑當婆離(十四)那茶羅(引)婆(引)私膩(十五)頭頭隷頭頭漏(十六)賒摩賒摩(十七)羶多(引)摩那賜(十八)除一切雨障莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三世諸佛真實力故大慈心故。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正行精進心故。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勅召一切諸大龍王莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅無邊海莊嚴威德輪蓋龍王。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅雖陀優波難陀龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅娑伽龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅阿耨達多龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅摩那斯龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅婆婁那龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅德叉迦龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅提頭賴吒龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅婆修吉龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅目真隣陀龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅伊羅跋那龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅分茶羅龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅大威光龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅威賢龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅電冠龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅大摩尼髻龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅戴摩尼髻龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅光髻龍王於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我勅是等一切龍王於閻浮提請雨國內。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "降澍大雨訖。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又說呪曰。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "那祇那祇瞿羅(引)摩(引)柰賜(三)那伽咥(喜梨反四)梨陀易頭摩鳩隷(五)郁伽羅盂路曬(六)波羅旃陀低豉(七)毘氀姞利(八)阿尸(引)毘師(九)阿咥(引)瞿(十)訖栗瑟那(去)崩(引)伽隷(十一)旃(引)遮隷(十二)盧羅(引)嗜薜(十三)摩訶頗那(引)呿隷呿羅(引)波施(十四)勞陀羅(引)波(引)尸膩(十五)頭沖薜(十六)波羅波羅(十七)庇利庇利(十八)富路富路(十九)毘私(引)哹(匹尤反)婁闍膩(二十)浮路浮路(二十一)摩訶蒲祇(二十二)摩尼達隷(二十三)匹利匹利(二十四)副漏副漏(二十五)破邏破邏(二十六)跋利沙跋利沙(二十七)閻藍浮(引)陀隷(二十八)睒浮睒浮(二十九)婆羅(引)訶翅(三十)那吒(引)碪薜(三十一)那吒(引)碪薜(三十二)忡忡忡忡薜(三十三)彌伽波羅(引)薜(三十四)彌伽婆(引)咥膩(三十五)茶迦茶迦茶迦(三十六)茶沈薜(三十七)伽那(去)伽那(去三十八)尸棄膩(三十九)迦那迦那(四十)伽那伽那(四十一)摩訶那伽(引)伽那(去四十二)尼囉(引)怛藍(四十三)糅(引)波闍羅(四十四)得迦紇唎(四十五)摩訶那伽(引)紇利陀(引)曳(四十六)瞿摩瞿摩瞿摩波(引)耶(四十七)頞悉低迦(引)承伽唎(四十八)浮承(引)伽彌(四十九)毘迦吒僧迦吒瞿隷(五十)毘私孚盧闍泥(五十一)毘折(時列反)林(引)婆泥(五十二)我今召集此會一切諸龍王等。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0499c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於閻浮提請雨國內降澍大雨。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸佛如來力故。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三世諸佛真實力故。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慈悲心故莎呵。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時世尊說此呪已告龍王言。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若天旱時欲請雨者。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其請雨主必於一切諸眾生等起慈悲心。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有比丘及比丘尼必須戒行本來清淨。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若曾違犯尼薩耆罪乃至眾學。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆須已前七日七夜殷重懺悔。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若在俗人亦須於前七日七夜。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "日別須受八關齋戒。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至請雨行道之日。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉須清淨無得懈慢。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當於空地實淨土上。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "除去沙礫無諸棘草。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "方十二步以為道場場中起壇方十步。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "壇高一尺用[牛*秦]牛糞。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "取新淨者周匝泥壇。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於壇中央施一高座。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "座上敷設新青淨褥張新青帳。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從高座東量三肘外。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "用牛糞汁畫作龍王一身三頭。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦畫彼龍左右眷屬圍遶。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "龍王從高座南量五肘外。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "畫作龍王一身五頭。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦畫諸龍左右圍遶。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從高座西量七肘外。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "畫作龍王一身七頭。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦畫諸龍左右圍遶。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從高座北量九肘外。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "畫作龍王一身九頭。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦畫諸龍左右圍遶。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其壇四角安四華瓶各容三升。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又以金精或復石黛。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "和水令清悉使瓶滿。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "種種華木諸雜華蘂插著瓶內。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "道場四門各各置一大妙香爐。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燒種種香熏陸沈水蘇合栴檀及安息等。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四角各懸青幡七枚。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "合二十八幡各長一丈。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然蘇油燈亦隨幡數。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設諸雜果蘇酪乳糜安置四面。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸龍王前散華燒香勿令斷絕。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其果飲食及以瓶水。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "日別使新不得隔宿。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "恒以晨朝日初出時施設供具。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "讀經之者一日三時香湯澡浴。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "著新青衣持齋靜思。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟食蘇酪及乳糜等粳米果菜。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若大小便又須澡浴。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昇高座時先禮十方一切諸佛。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燒香散花奉請十方一切諸佛諸大菩薩。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及以一切諸天龍王。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其誦呪人為護身故。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或呪淨水或呪白灰。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自心繫念以結場界。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或於一步乃至多步。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若水若灰用為界畔。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又呪縷綖為結。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "繫頂及以手足。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當呪水時散灑項上及灑額上。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應作是念。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有惡心者不得入此壇場界內。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其誦呪者於諸眾生恒起慈心勿生惡念。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又願以此禮佛念誦及諸功德。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迴施一切諸天龍王。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "并及含識有形之類。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昇法座時高聲讀誦此經及呪晝夜不絕。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若一七日若二七日。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遠至三七日必降甘雨。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "除不專念無慈心人及穢濁者。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告龍王。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "海水潮來尚可盈縮。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此言真實決定不虛。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸龍王蒙佛教已。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "歡喜踊躍頂禮奉行。",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大雲輪請雨經卷下",
        "from": "T19n0991_002:0500b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]